{"627690":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"Idle Champions of the Forgotten Realms","steam_appid":627690,"required_age":0,"is_free":true,"dlc":[3375180,3310360,3375170,3375150,3375160,3154750,1546840,1768120,1768130],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/627690\/extras\/AnimatedKeyArt_Final1_Small.gif?t=1746748841\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/627690\/extras\/SteamStorePage_AnimatedKeyArt_Logos.png?t=1746748841\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">招募传奇勇士，踏上无尽的终极冒险！<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">《Idle Champions of the Forgotten Realms》是一款策略管理游戏，将来自桌面角色扮演游戏战役、电子游戏、小说、实况游戏、漫画书和表演中的标志性勇士聚集在一起，展开一场宏大的冒险。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">用超过 140 名各具独特技能的勇士优化你的阵型，击败无数的怪物，完成数百次冒险。要精通这款游戏需要在每次冒险中不断推进阵型——只有最强大的阵型才能完成《Idle Champions》中最严峻的挑战。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/627690\/extras\/SteamStore_CollectIconicChampions_Chi.png?t=1746748841\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>收集标志性勇士<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">解锁来自整个《龙与地下城》宇宙的独特勇士，他们个个都有自己的阵型技能和杀招。粉丝们最爱的勇士包括崔斯特·杜垩登和秘银五侠、明斯克和布布、来自《博德之门 3》的阿斯代伦和卡菈克……以及很多很多其他勇士！<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/627690\/extras\/SteamStore_EasytoLearn_Chi.png?t=1746748841\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>上手很容易，精通很难<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">管理多支探险队，测试你手下勇士的勇气，并获取更丰厚的奖励。即使你关闭了游戏，你的勇士也会自动与敌人战斗，直到被打败为止。你的魔宠会自动进行基本的游戏操作，例如升级勇士和拾取金币，这样你就可以专心优化你的阵型策略。构建强大的协同效果，释放你手下勇士的全部力量，完成最困难的冒险吧！<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/627690\/extras\/SteamStore_Travel_Chi.png?t=1746748841\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>漫游《龙与地下城》多元宇宙<\/strong> <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">在剑湾和更遥远的地方展开冒险旅程。造访多座传奇名城，如博德之门、深水城和“众门之城”印记城。探索巴洛维亚的迷雾，于阿弗纳斯的无尽血战中冲杀，在星界之海中航行。<strong><\/strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/627690\/extras\/SteamStore_RegularContent_Chi.png?t=1746748841\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>定期内容更新<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">每月会有多次内容更新。《Idle Champions》自 2017 年推出以来，已经引入了 140 多名勇士，推出了超过 200 个冒险，以及根据官方桌面角色扮演游戏内容制作的 8 个战役，并在游戏中增添了数十项新功能和系统。下一个重大更新永远不会让你等太久！<\/p>","about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/627690\/extras\/AnimatedKeyArt_Final1_Small.gif?t=1746748841\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/627690\/extras\/SteamStorePage_AnimatedKeyArt_Logos.png?t=1746748841\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">招募传奇勇士，踏上无尽的终极冒险！<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">《Idle Champions of the Forgotten Realms》是一款策略管理游戏，将来自桌面角色扮演游戏战役、电子游戏、小说、实况游戏、漫画书和表演中的标志性勇士聚集在一起，展开一场宏大的冒险。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">用超过 140 名各具独特技能的勇士优化你的阵型，击败无数的怪物，完成数百次冒险。要精通这款游戏需要在每次冒险中不断推进阵型——只有最强大的阵型才能完成《Idle Champions》中最严峻的挑战。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/627690\/extras\/SteamStore_CollectIconicChampions_Chi.png?t=1746748841\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>收集标志性勇士<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">解锁来自整个《龙与地下城》宇宙的独特勇士，他们个个都有自己的阵型技能和杀招。粉丝们最爱的勇士包括崔斯特·杜垩登和秘银五侠、明斯克和布布、来自《博德之门 3》的阿斯代伦和卡菈克……以及很多很多其他勇士！<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/627690\/extras\/SteamStore_EasytoLearn_Chi.png?t=1746748841\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>上手很容易，精通很难